## Languages

🔤 Supported Languages
English (en)

Bahasa Indonesia (id)

Simplified Chinese (zh-hans)

Arabic (ar)

Change language using:

from smartsys_analyzer.config import set_language
set_language("id")  # or "en", "zh-hans", "ar"

🧪 Running Locally:

python -m smartsys_analyzer.core

or test each module:

python smartsys_analyzer/utils.py

